descriptionHtml: After several PM's and my own delusional mind decided to create yet another remake of Serana. If you have my Felicity mod you will notice I kinda hinted around (I'm known for this) at a Serana replacer when I uploaded a hair patch titled (Serana hair). I wanted this pair to actually look like Mother and Daughter so if you look close you can see the resemblance as I sculpted Valerica from Serana's facegen. Harken was left out because for me he says what a few lines and turns into well...you know. I also wanted the pair to be less involved in their fancy magic and more Melee and Ranged for their combat. They both, of course, will still use all three combat types well. Now, if you were like me and spent hours and hours going through the quest's to get the famous "Auriel's Bow" only to find out it is just as crappy as the basic Elven Bow then this mod is for you because they both have an enhanced version along with blood cursed arrows.
author: Kittyness
